{"tid":1547702,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"警狗最怕嘅係....","createTime":"2019-09-06T18:06:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T10:17:54.000Z","uid":259963,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ba967c48c4704fd88138c68cfbdcd35fc21b9291","tid":1547702,"uid":259963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T18:06:10.000Z","msg":"警狗好怕有人搞佢私人生活同埋屋企人<br />\n所以先會咁驚比人起底<br />\n<br />\n除左依樣，其實popo都好驚鬼神<br />\n好多popo都有玩神打<br />\n佢地以前做野好多時要接觸屍體果d<br />\n所以佢地好忌諱鬼神之說<br />\n我個黑警親戚做左幾廿碌，平時講野講到自己高高在上又串柒柒咁<br />\n一講到鬼神野佢即刻縮<br />\n<br />\n如果太子真係有人死左，popo一定會驚到鳩縮<br />\n可以嘅話，鬼神之說嘅野唔好上自己人page<br />\nSpread去藍絲page<br />\n幫popo製造真正嘅白色恐怖<br />\n要佢地生活係陰影之下<br />\n<br />\n如果新屋嶺真係有打死人<br />\n佢地一定會驚到拜神打齋乜都做齊"},{"pid":"fc30c74c05f4f2690c7a4c963f9df90cb5209918","tid":1547702,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T18:06:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一句講晒，睇哩個post</span></span><br />\n[置頂/請廣傳/多圖] 907 遊客LOOK 暢遊大嶼山指南<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1547426\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1547426</a>"},{"pid":"f04d2b0af85f2cc0f9284fd91ea9b9946f706dfa","tid":1547702,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T18:06:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e450121975692f66696781cd6d143efbf2af8a5c","tid":1547702,"uid":285368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T18:06:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pn0kzue.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPn0kzue.jpg&h=2228b3c7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e30b3a19e33e348a9df40a0a8ff49daf7aeb23ae","tid":1547702,"uid":285368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T18:07:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZabPsR5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZabPsR5.jpg&h=43c783c4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c8c0ea890baa20a8ddb0afdff9509ae3148158f7","